colss=list(data.columns)
colss.pop(0)
for m in colss:
    fig,axs=plt.subplots(2,2)
    count=1
    for i,j,k in zip(range(0,22,7),[[0,0],[0,1],[1,0],[1,1]],["blue","red","orange","green"]):
        a="tab"+":"+k
        count+=1
        if(count==5):
            x=datamay["Date_tmp"][i:i+7+3]
            y=datamay[m][i:i+7+3]
        else:
            
            x=datamay["Date_tmp"][i:i+7]
            y=datamay[m][i:i+7]
        axs[j[0],j[1]].plot(x,y,a)
        axs[0, 0].set_title(m)

colss=list(data.columns)
colss.pop(0)
for m in colss:
    count=1
    for i,j in zip(range(0,15,14),["orange","red"]):
        fig,(axs1,axs2)=plt.subplots(1,2)
        fig.suptitle(m)
        fig.tight_layout(pad=2.0)

        x1=datamay["Date_tmp"][i:i+7]
        y1=datamay[m][i:i+7]
        if(count==2):
            x2=datamay["Date_tmp"][i+7:i+14+3]
            y2=datamay[m][i+7:i+14+3]
        else:
            x2=datamay["Date_tmp"][i+7:i+14]
            y2=datamay[m][i+7:i+14]
        count+=1
        a="tab"+":"+j
        axs1.plot(x1,y1,a)
        axs1.fill_between(x1,0,y1,color=j)
        axs2.plot(x2,y2,a)
        axs2.fill_between(x2,0,y2,color=j)

new_cols=["Daily_Confirmed_Diff","Total_Confirmed_Diff","Daily_Recovered_Diff","Total_Recovered_Diff","Daily_Deceased_Diff","Total_Deceased_diff"]
existing_cols=list(datamay_diff.columns)
existing_cols.pop(0)
existing_cols
prv_vals=[1801,34866,630,9059,75,1154]
for i,j,l in zip(new_cols,existing_cols,prv_vals):
    datamay_diff[i]=list(range(len(datamay_diff)))
    datamay_diff[i][0]=datamay_diff[j][0]-l
    for k in range(0,len(datamay_diff)-1):
        datamay_diff[i][k+1]=datamay_diff[j][k+1]-datamay_diff[j][k]
